<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full" data-theme="light">
<%- include('partials/shell/head-start', { pageTitle: 'About - Paperless-AI next' }) %>
<%- include('partials/shell/head-end') %>
<%- include('partials/shell/body-open', {
    version: typeof version !== 'undefined' ? version : '',
    chatEnabled: typeof chatEnabled !== 'undefined' ? chatEnabled : false,
    ragEnabled: typeof ragEnabled !== 'undefined' ? ragEnabled : false
}) %>
            <div class="content-wrapper space-y-6">
                <div class="content-header">
                    <div class="content-header-main">
                        <h1 class="content-title">About this Fork</h1>
                        <p class="content-subtitle">Support information, project background, and author details.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="material-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">💖 Support the Project</h3>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-3 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            If you find this tool helpful, consider supporting its development:
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/admonstrator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub Sponsors" class="inline-flex">
                                <img class="no-invert" alt="GitHub Sponsors" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Sponsors-EA4AAA?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/admon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Buy Me A Coffee" class="inline-flex">
                                <img class="no-invert" alt="Buy Me A Coffee" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Buy%20Me%20A%20Coffee-FFDD00?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=buy-me-a-coffee&amp;logoColor=black">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://ko-fi.com/admon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Ko-fi" class="inline-flex">
                                <img class="no-invert" alt="Ko-fi" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Ko--fi-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://paypal.me/aaronviehl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="PayPal" class="inline-flex">
                                <img class="no-invert" alt="PayPal" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-00457C?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=paypal&amp;logoColor=white">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="material-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">System Information (Support)</h3>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>App Version:</strong> <%= supportInfo.appVersion %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Build Commit SHA:</strong> <span class="font-mono break-all"><%= supportInfo.commitSha %></span></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Node.js:</strong> <%= supportInfo.nodeVersion %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Platform:</strong> <%= supportInfo.platform %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Environment:</strong> <%= supportInfo.nodeEnv %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>AI Provider:</strong> <%= supportInfo.aiProvider %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Uptime:</strong> <%= supportInfo.uptime %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Server Time (UTC):</strong> <%= supportInfo.serverTimeUtc %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Server Timezone:</strong> <%= supportInfo.timezone %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>RAG Enabled:</strong> <%= supportInfo.ragEnabled ? 'yes' : 'no' %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Chat Enabled:</strong> <%= supportInfo.chatEnabled ? 'yes' : 'no' %></div>
                        <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50"><strong>Mistral OCR Enabled:</strong> <%= supportInfo.ocrEnabled ? 'yes' : 'no' %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="material-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Issue Reporting</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        Open a prefilled issue report with version and environment details, or copy diagnostics to your clipboard.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                        <a
                            id="openPrefilledIssueBtn"
                            href="https://github.com/admonstrator/paperless-ai-next/issues/new?template=bug_report.yml"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors text-sm"
                        >
                            <i class="fas fa-bug mr-2"></i>Open Issue Form
                        </a>
                        <button
                            id="copyIssueDiagnosticsBtn"
                            type="button"
                            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors text-sm"
                        >
                            <i class="fas fa-copy mr-2"></i>Copy Issue Details
                        </button>
                        <span id="issueHelperStatus" class="text-sm text-gray-500 self-center"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="material-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">This app is awesome because ✨</h3>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-3 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            No corporate blah blah - just useful stuff that makes daily document chaos easier to handle 😄
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                            <li>⚡ Faster dashboard and history pages → less waiting, more doing</li>
                            <li>🧠 Smarter OCR + AI fallback flows → fewer dead ends when documents are messy</li>
                            <li>🛡️ Stronger security defaults → safer setup out of the box</li>
                            <li>🐳 Cleaner Docker workflows → easier updates and less deployment pain</li>
                            <li>📊 Better status + failure visibility → you immediately see what needs attention</li>
                            <li>🧰 Practical support info page → easier bug reports and faster help</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            End result: smoother daily use, cool new features and more magic! 🌟
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ❤️ Big, fat thank you to the original project:
                            <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/clusterzx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@clusterzx</a>
                            and
                            <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/clusterzx/paperless-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">clusterzx/paperless-ai</a>.
                            This fork stands on that foundation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="material-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">About the Author 👋</h3>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                        <p>
                            Meet the maintainer behind this fork: <strong>admonstrator (Aaron Viehl)</strong> 🔥
                            (<a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/admonstrator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@admonstrator</a>)
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Aaron is all about building practical tools that actually help in daily operations:<br />
                            less noise, more reliability, smarter automation, fewer annoying edge-case surprises 💪<br />
                            Also known as “the grumpy nerd next door,” he is CTO at
                            <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://singleton-factory.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@singleton-factory</a>,
                            based in Germany.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Want updates, ideas, or just nerdy tech talk? 👇<br />
                            <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://admon.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">admon.me</a>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            I am a trained IT specialist for system integration, not a classic full-time software engineer — and yes,
                            I use AI heavily to move faster. But every change still gets human review, hands-on testing, and a lot of
                            iteration time from me until it is stable, practical, and trustworthy in daily use. If you find issues, have ideas, or want to contribute, please reach out! ❤️🙌
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script id="supportInfoPayload" type="application/json"><%- JSON.stringify(supportInfo || {}).replace(/</g, '\\u003c') %></script>

    <%- include('partials/scripts/about-scripts') %>
    <%- include('partials/shell/footer') %>
    <%- include('partials/shell/body-close') %>
